<h2 class="bold font-l">Salem's Lot '04 [Bus Full of Vampire Children]</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Scene from the mini-series 2004 version of Salem's Lot. Charlie Rhodes is a local school bus driver of the town, but likewise a noted jerkass to the kids he ferries. However once the vampires start acting more openly as the town comes more and more under Barlow's power. The kids who were turned decided to give him a taste of karma, as they go to taste Charlie's blood </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UndeadChild" class='trope-example-link'>Undead Child</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
